# Drop store photos here

Save your store photos as:
- store-1.jpg
- store-2.jpg
- store-3.jpg
- store-4.jpg
- store-5.jpg
- store-6.jpg

Each card on the marketing site auto-hides if its image isn't found,
so you can start with 1-2 and add more later.

Recommended: square or 4:3 aspect ratio, under 500 KB each (compress
at tinypng.com if larger).

Edit the store name and category for each card directly in
`index.html` — search for "Real stores. Real reviews."
